{"tid":9052,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"剛果民主共和國反華示威　「向中國人說不」","createTime":"2016-11-28T13:38:47.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T03:44:44.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fb25fc895bcc5a614e814315d3bd533a1a3b76eb","tid":9052,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T13:38:47.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=uYzQBpRLOc79lpwGqeW%2Bx8W%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=c2f609e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】中非國家剛果民主共和國首都金沙薩（Kinshasa）今日爆發了反華示威，有中學生因不滿教育部，欲將他們學校的一部分，交予當地中國大使館管理的計劃，而在教育部總部前遊行抗議，有學生更高舉「向中國人說不（no to the Chinese）」的標語。 <br />\n<br />\n從現場的相片可見，大量的中學生聚集到教育部附近示威請願，反對中國大使館接管他們學校的一部分。有警察在現場維持秩序，氣氛大致和平，學生的情緒看似亦相當平靜。 <br />\n<br />\n據了解，剛果民主共和國與中國有頗為密切的經濟關係。據悉，有中國礦產企業於本月計劃在剛果民主共和國投資設廠。"},{"pid":"1e1b2ff0b77f4509b7de255eb3bc7680f71f5214","tid":9052,"uid":25350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T13:45:17.000Z","msg":"支持推行普教剛"},{"pid":"5c842bbd4a1bd616db983841ba5e820a125134c2","tid":9052,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T13:59:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab54f4484f1c386c8d3c0d6f970fd503da858ae8","tid":9052,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T14:14:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a5c95359c0f669a4353769ff8586d2c027526b3","tid":9052,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:03:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08ff01579c681d4d64a93f732239289ada4d5457","tid":9052,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:05:42.000Z","msg":"全球反華指日可待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cd786ef6138ae9dca92fb8a69253ea99028fc96"